{"tid":56479,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊宣傳着錯衫　變招符碌警？","createTime":"2016-12-27T09:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T09:43:05.000Z","uid":53046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49050941a60b019a230f0e7363a7b7150084123c","tid":56479,"uid":53046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/172004_e6854af3eb0924f0a1d2412b76341b27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F172004_e6854af3eb0924f0a1d2412b76341b27.jpg&h=b5c619a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=VuPL272kMKFTdag9%2BRcrvoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=1db7c2c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a> 東網專訊】警隊將於今年1月14日展開新一輪招募，聘請新紥師兄，仲推出一連串宣傳攻勢，包括在各主要道路展示大型廣告牌，更成為警隊facebook的主題相片，圖中顯示一名軍裝警員及一名便衣警員正拼命追一名戴上口罩的賊人，相當有動感，似在拍攝<span style=\"color: red;\">Running Man。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，該幅宣傳廣告就引起網民熱烈討論，指軍裝警員的身型頗為肥胖，追賊時顯得頗為辛苦。更有眼利網民發現，便衣警員身穿的T恤上面寫上「<span style=\"color: red;\">FLUKE</span>」5個英文字母，諧音是「<span style=\"color: red;\">符碌</span>」！<br />\n<br />\n翻查字典，FLUKE的意思是「僥倖」，有網民戲謔，唔通今時今日做警察，一是要心存僥倖，一是要<span style=\"color: red;\">符碌</span>，其實一件T恤上的字眼，都是趣事一則！"},{"pid":"88d4ea911bc23eb3e17ac252ee930a5644b11d94","tid":56479,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:43:05.000Z","msg":"班警犬識春字咩"}]}